  "text": "The BED assay was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions with one exception, samples were run in duplicate and results were reported as mean normalized optical density units (Sedia Biosciences Corporation, Portland, OR, USA). The avidity assay, a modified version of the Genetic Systems HIV-1/HIV-2+ O EIA (Bio-Rad Laboratories, Redmond, WA), was performed as previously described [CITATION_1] .",
